Interface IChangeHistoryEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEvent, IWorkspaceEvent

    public interface IChangeHistoryEvent
extends IWorkspaceEvent
    Generic event type to describe the flow of change from or to a particular workspace connection.
